# Hackathon Submission: Bugbell

## GitHub handle
_Enter your GitHub handle_

@pscsdev

## Project Title
_What is the name of your project?_

Bugbell

## Project Description    
_What have you built during the hackathon?_

The project I created is a simple github issue notifier for your starred repos.

## Inspiration behind the Project  
_What is the story behind this project? Why did you choose to work on this specific idea?_

We spent a lot of time hopping between different repos to find that one "issue" we are interested to contribute to.

## Tech Stack    
_How have you built this project? Mention the technologies/methods/platforms you used to build your project_

Next.js
BetterAuth (I tried github oauth integration using appwrite but the docs are not well updated and I was facing the issue with appwrite github oauth for a while, so I switched to better-auth),
TailwindCSS, 
Appwrite Databases

